{"tid":1498970,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"823報告）街上面全部香港人 正 仆街","createTime":"2019-08-23T14:40:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T16:38:46.000Z","uid":208927,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"55d301fae2535dd174130d6f1d985815e42c7941","tid":1498970,"uid":208927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:40:00.000Z","msg":"街上面全部香港人，正！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wz6eemu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWz6eemu.jpg&h=3316508a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仆街，我本來只係踢拖諗住落樓下跟隊<br />\n條隊唔斷嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搞到我美孚行到去旺角<br />\n(我一開始真係諗住搵龍尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />行下行下到旺角太子）<br />\n<br />\n路面報告及檢討<br />\n路線：（長沙灣道）美孚至太子（彌敦道）<br />\n時間：1945-2110<br />\n<br />\n往荃灣方向行車線：<br />\n1.美孚新村&mdash;&gt;龍尾 長沙灣怡閣苑（九龍工業對面）<br />\n2.深水埗c1出口至龍尾 太子金都商場<br />\n（長沙灣道及荔枝角道交界）<br />\n<br />\n往尖沙嘴方向行車線：<br />\n3.龍頭 九龍工業學校&mdash;&gt;龍尾 南昌街（橫入南昌休憇處）<br />\n4.龍頭 太子道西&mdash;&gt; 龍尾 始創中心 （ 2110已經冇晒人 ）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PzHti2i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPzHti2i.jpg&h=681bf9e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n地圖右邊為尖沙嘴方向<br />\n黃色往尖沙嘴<br />\n紫紅往荃灣<br />\n<br />\n建議：<br />\n1.下次可以講定行車方向，等大家真正連成一線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.聽到有人不斷傳2040 唱咩歌/ 2100遮右眼<br />\n不如文宣盡量統一活動/ 口號循環+reset<br />\n到時大家開airdrop 互send, 身邊總有一個有<br />\n噤就可以一齊叫口號/ 唱歌<br />\n距離太遠唔同步就20分鐘reset一次<br />\ni.e<br />\n1. 5x 光復香港-&gt;5x五大訴求-&gt;5x香港人-&gt;5x黑警還眼...<br />\n1920/1940/2000正就重新開始，由光復香港開始<br />\n噤至少第光復香港，時代革命大家都係非常齊整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.所有司機大佬們請盡情㩒喇巴（最好有節奏的）<br />\nBtw 冇試過噤鍾意司機9響銨<br />\n<br />\n辛苦馬路嘅大家每次轉燈都走黎走去<br />\n香港人真高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b26ba0f7a02d9e1389f09defb2e0b8d55eabab","tid":1498970,"uid":208927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:41:11.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"9f36253732a67ec2054d26c698cfc1c48167a855","tid":1498970,"uid":209248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:41:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b549e6e03f513fe6948545e4239fd7fa454da87","tid":1498970,"uid":281475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:48:25.000Z","msg":"今晚真係好撚熱血"},{"pid":"00dff7dbc03fe1b297852a1ae5a06e96ceac11fc","tid":1498970,"uid":208927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b549e6e03f513fe6948545e4239fd7fa454da87","tid":1498970,"uid":281475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:48:25.000Z","msg":"今晚真係好撚熱血"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:50:13.000Z","msg":"其實好好<br />\n冇人會比人拉<br />\n又就腳<br />\n冇人敢搞事"},{"pid":"b575fec3159aed69be63ef28bd1db43aa51b6a17","tid":1498970,"uid":208927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:58:27.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"9cab9461d5f4e21202c96ded43dab09648206aee","tid":1498970,"uid":208927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:38:46.000Z","msg":"Up"}]}